title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show AUG-14-2013 WED

The Dennis Prager Radio Show AUG-14-2013 WED






Prager 20130814  03 Star

Prager H3: Ashton Kutcher offered kids some very good advice at the Teen Choice Awards

Prager 20130814  02 Male/Female Hour: The Perfect Moment

Prager H2: People put off marriage and then children waiting for the perfect moment.
 But there is never a perfect moment to accomplish either tasks.





Prager 20130814  01 Clown Show

Prager H1: An incident at the Missouri State Fair involving a clown and an Obama mask becomes
 a national incident. Can the President be lampooned? Or is he off limits?
